title: 88 Key Removable Piano Keyboard Note Labels,Silicone Reusable No Need Stickers,Notes Label for Beginners and Kids Comes (Black)
features: Anti-slip Noise Reduction: There are anti-slip lines on the back. The adsorption force is improved, which effectively prevents the fierce performance from shifting and warping; The silent design can meet your late-night practice without disturbing the people.

Silicone material: The piano sticker is made of food-grade liquid silicone, which is non-toxic and tasteless, non-irritating in long-term contact with the skin, and connects the label in series, no need to stick to the keys like a piano sticker.

Thoughtful design: Stickers fit snugly into the gaps of the piano keyboard, preventing dust and liquids, effectively extending the life of the keys, and dual staff displays the notes of each key, helping to find the corresponding keys from the keyboard faster

How to use: Installing our piano stickers is quick and easy. Simply clean the key surface and carefully place the silicone note strip on the key. No special tools or equipment are required and can be removed at any time.
Portable Storage: Comes with a waterproof storage box, the piano sticker is not stained when you go out, and the roll design saves space.
description: High-quality silicone material: ★Made of high-quality silicone, it has a soft and elastic texture that perfectly conforms to the curvature of the piano keys for a comfortable playing touch. ★It has excellent abrasion resistance and water resistance, is not easy to damage, and can effectively resist wear and stains in daily use, and prolong the service life. Good adhesion performance: ★The stickiness is moderate, the paste is firm, and it is not easy to fall off during playing, ensuring stability during use. ★At the same time, it is highly detachable, and if it is removed with a special cleaning agent, it will basically not leave glue stains on the keys and will not cause damage to the keys. Widely applicable scenarios: ★It is mainly suitable for 88-key pianos and electronic organs, whether it is a grand piano, an upright piano, or a digital piano, etc., it can be perfectly adapted. ★It is especially suitable for piano beginners, children and music lovers, helping them to become familiar with the key position faster, improve learning efficiency and playing accuracy.
